'''紐約都會區'''，也被称为'''三州地区'''，是全[[美國|美國]]最大的[[都會區|都會區]]，也是全世界最大都會區之一，位于[[美國東北部|美國東北部]]。

整個都會區以[[紐約市|紐約市]]為中心，包括[[紐約州|紐約州]][[紐約上州|上州]]的六個郡與[[長島_(紐約)|長島]]的兩個郡，[[紐澤西州|紐澤西州]]的十四個郡，[[康乃狄克州|康乃狄克州]]的三個郡，以及[[賓夕法尼亞州|賓夕法尼亞州]]東北部的一個郡所組成。全部地區由城區與郊區所組成。

根据2015年[[美国人口调查局|美国人口调查局]]的估计，纽约都会区仍然以相当大的差距位居美国人口最多的地区，不管是定义的大都会统计区（2020万人口）<ref name=MetroEst>{{cite web|url=http://factfinder.census.gov/bkmk/table/1.0/en/PEP/2015/GCTPEPANNR.US24PR|title=Annual Estimates of the Resident Population: April 1, 2010 to July 1, 2015 – Metropolitan Statistical Area; and for Puerto Rico – 2015 Population Estimates|publisher=U.S. Census Bureau|accessdate=2016-03-28|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200213004926/http://factfinder.census.gov/bkmk/table/1.0/en/PEP/2015/GCTPEPANNR.US24PR|archive-date=2020-02-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref>还是联合统计区（2370万人口）；<ref name=CombinedEst>{{cite web|url=http://factfinder.census.gov/bkmk/table/1.0/en/PEP/2015/GCTPEPANNR.US41PR|title=Annual Estimates of the Resident Population: April 1, 2010 to July 1, 2015 – Combined Statistical Area; and for Puerto Rico – 2015 Population Estimates|publisher=U.S. Census Bureau|accessdate=2016-03-28|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200213005001/http://factfinder.census.gov/bkmk/table/1.0/en/PEP/2015/GCTPEPANNR.US41PR|archive-date=2020-02-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref>它也是世界上人口最多的城市群之一，以及[[北美洲|北美洲]]最大的城市群。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mongabay.com/cities_urban_01.htm|title=World's Largest Urban Areas [Ranked by Urban Area Population]|publisher=Rhett Butler|year=2003–2006|accessdate=2011-11-25|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=http://arquivo.pt/wayback/20091009143739/http://www.mongabay.com/cities_urban_01.htm|archivedate=2009年10月9日}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.worldatlas.com/citypops.htm|title=Largest Cities of the World – (by metro population)|publisher=Woolwine-Moen Group d/b/a Graphic Maps|accessdate=2011-11-25|archive-date=2016-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160618031809/http://www.worldatlas.com/citypops.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.demographia.com/db-wlargestua.pdf|title=Largest urban areas in the world: 2008 All Urban Areas 2,000,000 & Over|publisher=Wendell Cox Consultancy|accessdate=2011-11-25|archive-date=2012-09-12|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6AdLNiOvc?url=http://www.demographia.com/db-wlargestua.pdf|dead-url=yes}}</ref>纽约都会区继续成为向美国合法移民的首要门户，<ref name=Immigrants2013est>{{cite web|url=https://www.dhs.gov/yearbook-immigration-statistics-2013-lawful-permanent-residents|title=Yearbook of Immigration Statistics: 2013 Lawful Permanent Residents Supplemental Table 2|publisher=U.S. Department of Homeland Security|accessdate=2014-07-31|archive-date=2016-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161013214828/https://www.dhs.gov/yearbook-immigration-statistics-2013-lawful-permanent-residents|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Immigrants2012est>{{cite web|url=https://www.dhs.gov/yearbook-immigration-statistics-2012-legal-permanent-residents|title=Yearbook of Immigration Statistics: 2012 Supplemental Table 2|publisher=U.S. Department of Homeland Security|accessdate=2014-07-31|archive-date=2015-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150624030947/http://www.dhs.gov/yearbook-immigration-statistics-2012-legal-permanent-residents|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Immigrants2011est>{{cite web|url=https://www.dhs.gov/files/statistics/publications/LPR11.shtm|title=Yearbook of Immigration Statistics: 2011 Supplemental Table 2|publisher=U.S. Department of Homeland Security|accessdate=2014-07-31|archive-date=2012-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120808080130/http://www.dhs.gov/files/statistics/publications/LPR11.shtm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Immigrants2010est>{{cite web|url=https://www.dhs.gov/files/statistics/publications/LPR10.shtm|title=Yearbook of Immigration Statistics: 2010 Supplemental Table 2|publisher=U.S. Department of Homeland Security|accessdate=2014-07-31|archive-date=2012-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120712200141/https://www.dhs.gov/files/statistics/publications/LPR10.shtm|dead-url=no}}</ref>拥有世界上任何大都会地区最多的外国出生人口。 都会统计区覆盖17,405平方公里，联合统计区面积34,493平方公里，涵盖种族和地理上不同的地区。 纽约都会区的人口比纽约州的人口多，而且到2016年，大都会区[[领空|领空]]的乘客人数已达1.3亿。<ref name=NYMetroAirspace>{{cite web|url=http://www.panynj.gov/airports/pdf-traffic/ATR2016.pdf|title=The Port Authority of NY and NJ 2016 Air Traffic Report|publisher=The Port Authority of New York and New Jersey|date=2017-04-14|accessdate=2017-06-26|6=|archive-date=2017-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170525172312/http://www.panynj.gov/airports/pdf-traffic/ATR2016.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

作为许多行业的中心，包括金融、[[国际贸易|国际贸易]]、新型传统媒体、房地产、教育、时尚、[[娱乐产业|娱乐]]、旅游、生物技术和制造业，纽约市都会区是世界最重要的经济区域之一；在2015年，都会统计区<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.whitehouse.gov/sites/default/files/omb/bulletins/2013/b13-01.pdf |title=Revised Delineations of Metropolitan Statistical Areas, Micropolitan Statistical Areas, and Combined Statistical Areas, and Guidance on Uses of the Delineations of These Areas – page 106 |publisher=Executive Office of the President  Office of Management and Budget |accessdate=2014-06-27 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130319014514/http://www.whitehouse.gov/sites/default/files/omb/bulletins/2013/b13-01.pdf |archivedate=2013-03-19 }}</ref>产生了将近1.6兆美元的生产总值（GMP）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.statista.com/statistics/183808/gmp-of-the-20-biggest-metro-areas/|title=Gross Metropolitan Product (GMP) of the United States in 2013, by metropolitan area (in billion current U.S. dollars)|publisher=Statista|accessdate=2014-09-12|archive-date=2014-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141005201511/http://www.statista.com/statistics/183808/gmp-of-the-20-biggest-metro-areas/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而在2015年，联合统计区的GMP超过了1.83兆美元，均位居全国第一，两者分别仅次于9个国家和7个国家的[[GDP|GDP]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.usmayors.org/metroeconomies/2013/201311-report.pdf |title=U.S. Metro Economies (note CSA 2012 GMP total includes sum of New York, Bridgeport, New Haven, Scranton, Trenton, Poughkeepsie, and Kingston MSA 2012 GMP values cited) |pages=9 through 18 in Appendix Tables |publisher=IHS Global Insight, The United States Conference of Mayors, and The Council on Metro Economies and the New American City |date=November 2013 |accessdate=2014-06-27 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150305224230/http://www.usmayors.org/metroeconomies/2013/201311-report.pdf |archivedate=2015-03-05 }}</ref>

